---
title: Pan-Seared Pork Chops with Summer Vegetable Kebabs & Oregano-Mint Pesto
description: Oregano and mint ought to get to know each other more, because we think they make a great couple. Spooned over juicy, pan-seared pork chops, this bright and tangy pesto truly shines. If you've never roasted lemons before, you're in for a treat: they become sweet and juicy in the oven, perfect for squeezing over caramelized veggies.
